{"tid":334880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"基本法教材稱港為「示威之都」　楊潤雄：專業角度出發　羅列社會意見","createTime":"2017-07-25T06:22:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-25T06:59:30.000Z","uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0473d05350edc9828dbdf70cadc687201fd93fbe","tid":334880,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T06:22:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170725/s00001/1500960111495\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170725%2Fs00001%2F1500960111495&d=Ynlc5qP%2BAAiannsWr8klettKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=34590d57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170725%2Fs00001%2F1500960111495&h=812df534\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170725/s00001/1500960111495</a><br />\n<br />\n教育局上月公布《中學教育課程指引》，要求於初中以51小時教授《基本法》，更於獨立單元教材中，提及基本法下港人的權利與義務時形容香港是「示威之都」。教育局長楊潤雄回應指，局方公開地將社會人士對基本法的意見羅列於教材中，希望透過教師的引導增加中小學生對基本法認識。<br />\n<br />\n教育局長楊潤雄今早被問到會否令人覺得教材有偏頗時稱，局方製作《基本法》教材時，是從公開、專業角度出發，「大家如果有留心去看，我們都公開地將社會人士對《基本法》的意見羅列於教材中」。<br />\n同時，楊潤雄稱局方嘗試從多角度，把市民對《基本法》可能比較不清晰的地方羅列出來，並希望透過課堂上教師的專業引導，令中、小學生，更加能夠理解《基本法》的內容。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄稱，制作教材時，除了在社會搜集資訊外，亦會與相關的專業團體討論，如有需要，會增潤教材內容完善教與學過程。<br />\n至於副局長人選方面，他重申仍在物色副局長人選，有決定將盡快公布。"},{"pid":"e8fceafb70c3ef1797debd8d8098956c4fbbb34b","tid":334880,"uid":112622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T06:24:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b7b2499ba76e510082180634f7be445c467e240","tid":334880,"uid":521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T06:34:35.000Z","msg":"奴才之都"},{"pid":"14b240f1dd7845b3f595631f5fad7a22ca9e583f","tid":334880,"uid":23058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T06:36:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://whatscap.ristury.com/java/WhatsCAP/content/photo/v1/48849_WM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwhatscap.ristury.com%2Fjava%2FWhatsCAP%2Fcontent%2Fphoto%2Fv1%2F48849_WM.jpg&h=7cd6e121&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7844110f684d8dbb74d664630e4e9bd703760e7c","tid":334880,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T06:50:04.000Z","msg":"撚人之都"},{"pid":"904290c35497146c235b934c35c58ab16684343b","tid":334880,"uid":895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T06:59:30.000Z","msg":"示威之都？<br />\n示弱之都咋話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}